name: harshnagoriya/Compiler-Design
description: A compiler translates the code written in one language to some other language without changing the meaning of the program. It is also expected that a compiler should make the target code efficient and optimized in terms of time and space. It includes lexical, syntax, and semantic analysis as front end, and code generation and optimization as back-end.
